		<label>ancient gene assembler</label>
		<description>A workbench for creating implantable xenogerms from genepacks stored in nearby gene banks. This device has collapsed in on itself, rendering it useless.</description>
		<size>(3,2</size>
		<fillPercent>0.50</fillPercent>

		<graphicData>
			<texPath>Things/Building/AG_GeneAssembler</texPath>
